PRIVACY POLICY

Last Updated: June 2026

Bedroom to Billboard ("the Game") is developed and operated by TonyIsrael.

This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when you use Bedroom to Billboard.

Information We Collect

Bedroom to Billboard does not require users to create an account.

Bedroom to Billboard does not collect personal information such as:

- Names
- Email addresses
- Phone numbers
- Physical addresses
- Location data

Game Data

The Game saves player progress locally on the user's device. Game progress, achievements, settings, and purchases may be stored on the device to improve gameplay experience.

Advertising

Bedroom to Billboard may display advertisements provided by third-party advertising partners, including Google AdMob.

Advertising providers may automatically collect certain non-personal information, including:

- Device information
- Advertising identifiers
- App usage information
- Diagnostic information

This information is used to display relevant advertisements and improve advertising services.

In-App Purchases

Bedroom to Billboard offers optional in-app purchases. These purchases may include premium content, virtual currency, energy upgrades, feature unlocks, and other game enhancements.

All purchases are processed securely through Google Play and are subject to Google's payment policies.

Future updates may introduce additional premium content and purchase options.

Children's Privacy

Bedroom to Billboard does not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe that a child has provided personal information through the Game, please contact us so that appropriate action can be taken.

Third-Party Services

The Game may use third-party services including:

- Google Play Services
- Google AdMob
- Google Play Billing

These services may collect certain technical information according to their own privacy policies.

Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect user data stored within the Game. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is completely secure.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any updates will be posted through updated versions of this policy.

